room_title: Escape room "Toys in the Attic" by Epic Escape Game in Muncie
room_description: You just inherited your great aunt's old house. Rummaging around in the attic, the door slams shut and you are locked in. All you see is old toys. Then you remember your great aunt always said: "The robot holds the key." Now it makes sense. Find the robot, get the key and unlock the door. Remember, toys can play too.
